36
00:02:57,852 --> 00:02:59,513
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa aku sungguh mati?</font>

37
00:03:01,083 --> 00:03:02,322
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah kau sudah melihatnya?</font>

38
00:03:04,953 --> 00:03:06,053
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak mungkin.</font>

39
00:03:06,493 --> 00:03:09,293
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo. Perjalanan kita masih panjang.</font>

40
00:03:20,673 --> 00:03:22,602
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, sedang apa?</font>

41
00:03:40,192 --> 00:03:41,692
<font color=#FFFF00>Ingatlah kematian.</font>

42
00:03:42,263 --> 00:03:45,863
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami selalu ada di sisi kalian.</font>

