50
00:04:02,442 --> 00:04:03,513
<font color=#FFFF00>Di sana.</font>

51
00:04:04,553 --> 00:04:07,213
<font color=#FFFF00>Aish! Dia kan tidak perlu mendorong sekeras itu. Sakit.</font>

52
00:04:07,513 --> 00:04:09,222
<font color=#FFFF00>Omong-omong, ke mana dia?</font>

53
00:04:10,252 --> 00:04:11,523
<font color=#FFFF00>Joon Oppa.</font>

54
00:04:13,592 --> 00:04:14,893
<font color=#FFFF00>Detektif Han.</font>

55
00:04:15,793 --> 00:04:17,493
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga! Astaga!</font>

56
00:04:26,002 --> 00:04:27,103
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa itu?</font>

57
00:04:38,452 --> 00:04:40,312
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo? Keadaan darurat.</font>

58
00:04:47,923 --> 00:04:50,262
<font color=#FFFF00>Murid dari SMP S, Pelajar Kim,</font>

59
00:04:50,262 --> 00:04:53,062
<font color=#FFFF00>mengakhiri hidupnya dengan meloncat
